data.text:
An Alabama marriage for Minnie Marx on 08 Dec 1880 in Marengo [County], Alabama to

Spouse Maurice Woolner [sic] is hers. It was performed by A. Mase, Rabbi of Mobile.

The 1900 Census New Orleans Ward 12, Orleans, Louisiana she is listed as born in Oct 1859 in Alabama. She is a widow. She was married in 1880.

Her 1910 passport application stated she was born in Demopolis, Alabama about 26 Oct 1859. She was living with her daughter Juliette and son-in law in Marvin Beach, South Norwalk, CT

In 1920 She was still in Norwalk with David L and Juliette Davis and her grandson John age 6.
